{
  "stem": "24163.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "First I was on the board.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then [BACKGROUND NOISE] for five years, I served as the president of Congregation Habonim.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Today it's Ezra-Habonim.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm still a member of Ezra-Habonim.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I am also-- most of our activities, religious ones, are with Rodfei Zedek, the Hyde Park Congregation.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, I, am doing-- because of my business affiliations in the neighborhood, I was president of the Chamber of Commerce for a number of years, and--",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, correct.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I served on the boards of Savings and Loan Association.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I have been a member of some of the local organizations.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I've also been a member of American Jewish Congress, of B'nai B'rith, ORT, the JCC, and other Jewish organizations for many, many years.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And JUF, of course.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And HIAS.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We, we lived here after I came home from the service.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then we moved to the South Shore area, where we had a lovely house for a number of years, or at least 10 years.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we decided to move back to Hyde Park.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We sold the house.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we lived in this apartment, which is very comfortable, ever since.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "About 27 years, I think, we've lived in this apartment now.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "East End, 5000 East End, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I think Hitler's coming to power changed our life completely.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As I've mentioned earlier on in detail, the changes, I probably would have gone on through high school and more than likely, attended the university in Germany, which is what middle class Jewish parents-- like they do today, here in the states, just as well-- ask their children to do.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I would have probably been some sort of an academic.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think, I think my parents wanted me to be an attorney, I believe so.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
